ttps:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Vai_tro_quan_trong_cua_bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang\" title=\"Vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang\">Vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Doi_voi_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-4'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Khang_dinh_dang_cap_thuong_hieu\" title=\"Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\">Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Truyen_tai_tot_tinh_than_thuong_hieu\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t tinh th\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u\">Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t tinh th\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-4'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Tang_su_trung_thanh_cua_khach_hang\" title=\"T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Doi_voi_khach_hang\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang_gom_nhung_gi\" title=\"B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?\">B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#_1_Yeu_to_nhan_dien_co_ban\" title=\"\u00a01. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n\">\u00a01. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#2_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_van_phong\" title=\"2. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng\">2. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#3_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_marketing\" title=\"3. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u marketing\">3. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u marketing<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#4_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_ngoai_troi\" title=\"4. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi\">4. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu-thoi-trang.html\/#5_Cac_ung_dung_nhan_dien_dac_thu_khac\" title=\"5. C\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 kh\u00e1c\">5. C\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 kh\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>\u1ede b\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho b\u1ea1n <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/thiet-ke-bo-nhan-dien-thuong-hieu.html\/\">b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/a> v\u00e0 g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng ri\u00eang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. C\u00f9ng \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp <strong>b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang\u00a0<\/strong>c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 g\u00ec nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9156\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/708a7e66241211.5b677b19413a6-300x150.jpg\" alt=\"b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang\" width=\"851\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/708a7e66241211.5b677b19413a6-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/708a7e66241211.5b677b19413a6-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/708a7e66241211.5b677b19413a6-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/708a7e66241211.5b677b19413a6.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vai_tro_quan_trong_cua_bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang\"><\/span><strong>Vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi_voi_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang\"><\/span><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Khang_dinh_dang_cap_thuong_hieu\"><\/span><strong>Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, gi\u00fap cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, th\u00ec nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u00f3. Ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong ng\u00e0nh th\u1eddi trang nh\u01b0 Louis, Vuitton, Chanel, Dior, Prada\u00a0 hay Gucci lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Truyen_tai_tot_tinh_than_thuong_hieu\"><\/span><strong>Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t tinh th\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n, t\u00ednh quy chu\u1ea9n cao trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u t\u1eeb m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, logo, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, phong c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc ri\u00eang, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap cho vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec3n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tang_su_trung_thanh_cua_khach_hang\"><\/span><strong>T\u0103ng s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang, \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u00e0m n\u00ean s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1edf ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0 c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. H\u1ecd t\u1ea1o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng kh\u00e2u ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, t\u1eeb th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ch\u1ea5t ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m gia t\u0103ng l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1eddi trang v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Doi_voi_khach_hang\"><\/span><strong>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u khi mua \u0111\u1ed3 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 khu trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i hay showroom n\u00e0o.<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m g\u00e1c t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1eddi trang \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/li>\n<li>T\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_thoi_trang_gom_nhung_gi\"><\/span><strong>B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_1_Yeu_to_nhan_dien_co_ban\"><\/span><strong>\u00a01. Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/brand-name-la-gi.html\/\"><strong>Brand name <\/strong><\/a>(t\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u): \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ecdc, d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ri\u00eang. V\u00ed d\u1ee5: Chanel, Gucci, Dior, Prada,..<\/p>\n<p><strong>Slogan<\/strong>(c\u00e2u kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u) l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn, s\u00fac t\u00edch truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u00fang th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u mu\u1ed3n truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i.<br \/>\nV\u00ed d\u1ee5: Slogan c\u1ee7a Canifa \u201cFashion for all\u201d \u2013 Th\u1eddi trang cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br \/>\nSlogan c\u1ee7a Nem \u2013 V\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 th\u1eddi trang Ph\u00e1p<br \/>\nSlogan c\u1ee7a CK Jean: \u201cBe good, Be bad, Be yourself\u201d- D\u00f9 t\u1ed1t, d\u00f9 x\u1ea5u, h\u00e3y l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea1n<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/5-buoc-thiet-ke-logo.html\/\"><strong>Logo <\/strong><\/a>l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, n\u00f3 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, logo ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, mang \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, thu h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_van_phong\"><\/span><strong>2. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u trong c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. N\u00f3 g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 danh thi\u1ebfp, gi\u1ea5y m\u1eddi, thi\u1ec7p ch\u00fac m\u1eebng,m\u1eabu h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n, th\u1ebb nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean, l\u1ecbch, banner,\u2026\u2026..<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_marketing\"><\/span><strong>3. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u marketing<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n b\u00e1 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. N\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m: website, fanpage Facebook, banner, profile, catalogue,\u2026<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Bo_nhan_dien_thuong_hieu_ngoai_troi\"><\/span><strong>4. B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1eabn gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c,\u00a0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n c\u1ea3 bi\u1ec3n qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o, bi\u1ec3n v\u1eaby, banner, poster, t\u1edd r\u01a1i,\u2026<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Cac_ung_dung_nhan_dien_dac_thu_khac\"><\/span><strong>5. C\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 kh\u00e1c<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1eddi ng\u00e0nh th\u1eddi trang, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 trang ph\u1ee5c, ph\u1ee5 ki\u1ec7n, v\u00ec v\u1eady B\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 g\u1ed3m: t\u00fai x\u00e1ch, nh\u00e3n m\u00e1c qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o, trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u1ee5c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean theo m\u00e0u th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. C\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean c\u00e1c nh\u00e3n m\u00e1c qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o, t\u00fai \u0111\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u1eddi trang \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><em>Ng\u00e0nh th\u1eddi trang l\u00e0 ng\u00e0nh lu\u00f4n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, do \u0111\u00f3\u00a0<strong>b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u th\u1eddi trang\u00a0<\/strong>c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd. N\u1ebfu doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 th\u1eafc m\u1eafc v\u1ec1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p th\u1eafc m\u1eafc.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u1ede b\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho b\u1ea1n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 g\u1ed3m c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ed7i ng\u0